window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Before Immortal Ascendants, worlds shatter like glass upon an anvil.</p> <p>Overhead, ancient golems awaken to cull the world of elves. To the east, the Cult of the Unblinking Eye plans the Hearthwood Clan's destruction. And beyond the bounds of time and space lurks greater threats than anyone could ever imagine.</p> <p>Chaos and ruin are all the awaits the World of Sanctuary and Serenity. Only one man can save it. And save it he must, for on that world lies everything he knows and loves.</p> <p>Theo must rise to greater heights than ever before. Join him for one final adventure as fate itself turns against him.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
